{"tid":2110643,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"往上層理論：唔好要大家難做  勸服惡客戴罩 車長獲激讚","createTime":"2020-07-16T05:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T05:23:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0f86f2f4b7650c7adf5bc99532dd5ebe1d082284","tid":2110643,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:15:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200716/34SVVA65RWJEIPORGN2LWOMPWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2F34SVVA65RWJEIPORGN2LWOMPWI%2F&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n3%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=f63791a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2F34SVVA65RWJEIPORGN2LWOMPWI%2F&h=23ea9715\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200716/34SVVA65RWJEIPORGN2LWOMPWI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n往上層理論：唔好要大家難做 <br />\n勸服惡客戴罩 車長獲激讚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【武肺再爆發】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎第三波疫情來襲，政府昨起強制所有公共交通乘客戴口罩，違者罰5,000元，隨。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n前晚一輛由青衣駛往元朗朗屏的68A線九巴上，一名男乘客登上巴士時未有戴口罩，車長勸喻，惟他不理會，逕自走往上層。乘客李小姐向本報提供片段並講述經過，指涉事無罩男乘客在福來邨永樂樓登上巴士，引起車上乘客恐慌及不滿，擔心會散播疫病。車長見狀立即拉上手掣，將巴士停泊好，之後到上層勸喻該乘客戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mJIGswayOgmdGVWulaQJjf9Md8Y=/794x585/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BZI7MWPBWDKHVLTQCAB3AUQDUE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmJIGswayOgmdGVWulaQJjf9Md8Y%3D%2F794x585%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBZI7MWPBWDKHVLTQCAB3AUQDUE.gif&h=3c69790d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名男乘客登上九巴時因未有戴口罩並逕自走往上層（左圖），車長作出勸喻近五分鐘，該乘客最終戴回口罩（右圖）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乘客惡言相向僵持五分鐘<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：撤關稅寬免勢打擊轉口地位<br />\n<br />\n惟該名男乘客屢勸不聽，李小姐指當時車長很有耐心勸喻，「你𠵱家係咪要阻住大家？」更指若對方拒絕戴罩，他便不會開車，只能報警處理，「你戴番個口罩我咪落去開車囉，唔好要大家難做！」男乘客一度惡言相向，僵持約五分鐘。惟車長堅持下，該男乘客最終軟化，萬分不情願下將手上的口罩戴上，事件才告一段落。李小姐認為涉事車長的做法十分值得表揚，保障了其他乘客安全。<br />\n<br />\n不過，同樣因口罩問題，車長未必可以勸服乘客，反。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有不願透露姓名的車長慨嘆，常碰到不戴口罩乘客，勸喻對方戴口罩時往往被反駁：。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/d1oxKP_rEm8t4xCAYMqY6vFIPJg=/420x710/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PVRR6XQXBAWHGGLBMEUBYLJD3Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fd1oxKP_rEm8t4xCAYMqY6vFIPJg%3D%2F420x710%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPVRR6XQXBAWHGGLBMEUBYLJD3Q.gif&h=7304dbca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n口罩令首日九巴五度報警<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。九巴表示截至昨午5時30分，共接獲五宗個案因乘客未有佩戴口罩，屢勸無效下報警的個案。<br />\n<br />\n九巴強調會落實遵守公共交通乘客須佩戴口罩的規定，並已向前線員工發出內部指引，如遇乘客未有佩戴口罩，車長可根據法例要求乘客戴上口罩。如乘客拒絕依從法例，車長可拒絕讓乘客上車，或在安全情況下要求他們下車，車長亦可向公司或警方尋求協助。"},{"pid":"0173a1fddb65cc716eb07cda5b55998fc76af61c","tid":2110643,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:16:51.000Z","msg":"柄埋邊打爆條撚樣就岩"},{"pid":"231e070ecaeb24012ac49e9730213b2e48b5d747","tid":2110643,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:16:58.000Z","msg":"下次直接報狗拉尻佢算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f320ade9fb7035bd98fb355c57e68fbaf5cf8cb","tid":2110643,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:20:16.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c4e0aa72c0c2e6a1b3690bab796b7e3e9260d1","tid":2110643,"uid":133806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0173a1fddb65cc716eb07cda5b55998fc76af61c","tid":2110643,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:16:51.000Z","msg":"柄埋邊打爆條撚樣就岩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:20:48.000Z","msg":"port台劈車啦<br />\n大家唔使搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41805f2495e167c0680ff7df52e4b1ca5b0295b","tid":2110643,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:22:18.000Z","msg":"借位求推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【投訴師請入】用 老任的法槌 制裁 亂港小精靈圖鑑<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2110642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2110642</a>"},{"pid":"18d7775f51434cea8abb136687befd358805f2a5","tid":2110643,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:23:32.000Z","msg":"中國人是要管的"}]}